{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2612828, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {"h": 431, "w": 668}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 498633, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re : ", "timestamp": 1632794136, "type": "image", "url": "6o/6o5ccozawl6p2fcoiuszu5kzx4c2oqbt.jpeg"}, {"cid": 2612829, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 498633, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "4个方向都可以，建议百度", "timestamp": 1632794147, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2612900, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 498633, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "好像不能用间距理解吧，margin也是往盒子上加厚边边。元素的排列是把整个盒子的大小都算出来然后排。", "timestamp": 1632794822, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2613117, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 498633, "reply_to": 2612828, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 就比如这个图，在border之内的区域背景都是红色的，可以区分。那这里margin起什么作用呢，是和哪里的距离呢，是和整个网页边框的距离吗😢", "timestamp": 1632797262, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2613124, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 498633, "reply_to": 2612900, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 那加了一个厚边边起什么作用呀，显示出来的不是只有border以内的区域嘛", "timestamp": 1632797325, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2613176, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 498633, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: border和background应该是不包括margin区域", "timestamp": 1632797984, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2613188, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 498633, "reply_to": 2613124, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 如果不设置border，background-color，padding和margin在显示上没啥区别", "timestamp": 1632798093, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2613252, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 498633, "reply_to": 2613188, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 对的没有背景时候margin和padding不影响呈现效果。但是调整margin后会明显让我这个block发生移动，我试了好多次都不知道这个使block发生移动的机制是什么，粗浅的感觉margin控制的是和其他盒子的距离？", "timestamp": 1632798607, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 6, "pid": 498633, "reply": 8, "tag": null, "text": "我在做html网页时候一直有问题不理解，想问问大家~网页中div是块级元素，他的大小由本身内容宽度加上padding宽度。那么margin作用是什么呢，定义上margin是块级元素之间的间距，但是如果一个页面上有很多块级元素，那么margin到底是和哪个元素的间距呢", "timestamp": 1632793999, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1632798608, "url": "", "vote": {}}}